OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782483502
OL,3,CMP 'shocked' by Home Office plan to
OL,4,Chouse migrants at military base
OL,6,FPlans to house asylum seekers at a
OL,7,Fmilitary base in Oxfordshire are
OL,8,F''shocking and worrying'', according
OL,9,Fto the local MP.
OL,11,FThe Home Office has announced it will
OL,12,Fseek planning permission to use
OL,13,FMinistry of Defence land in Bicester
OL,14,Ffor migrant accommodation.
OL,16,FThe site ` along with two others in
OL,17,FSuffolk and North Yorkshire ` could
OL,18,Feventually hold up to 3,750 asylum
OL,19,Fseekers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
