OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782483502
OL,3,CMP 'shocked' by Home Office plan to
OL,4,Chouse migrants at military base
OL,6,FBicester and Woodstock MP, Calum
OL,7,FMiller, told ITV News Meridian: "My
OL,8,Fmain concern at the moment is the lack
OL,9,Fof warning from the Home Office and
OL,10,Fthe lack of evidence they have
OL,11,Fprovided to me and the local community
OL,12,Fas to why this is justified.
OL,14,F"We need to know about cost, whether
OL,15,Fthis represents value for the
OL,16,Ftaxpayer. We need to know what will be
OL,17,Fdone to protect local residents, what
OL,18,Fsecurity arrangements will be put in
OL,19,Fplace. And what regime twill be put in
OL,20,Fplace to keep those within the site
OL,21,Fsafe."
OL,26,@oD@aOUvD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
