FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782483502
OL,3,CMP 'shocked' by Home Office plan to
OL,4,Chouse migrants at military base
OL,6,FThe Lib Dem politician added: "Only
OL,7,Fwhen we've had realistic answers to
OL,8,Fthose questions will we be in any
OL,9,Fposition to respond formally to this.
OL,10,FBut my insists are shock and worry
OL,11,Fabout whether this is right for our
OL,12,Fcommunity."
OL,14,FMr Miller urged local residents to
OL,15,F"react in a sober way" and said he
OL,16,Fwould be holding a meeting of local
OL,17,Fagencies to discuss the plans next
OL,18,Fweek.
OL,26,@nD@_OUtD@KO]wD@AOUwD@VO]
