PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782483502
OL,3,CMP 'shocked' by Home Office plan to
OL,4,Chouse migrants at military base
OL,6,FThe vast MOD Bicester site is a
OL,7,Flogistics hub and has been home to a
OL,8,Fnumber of different military units
OL,9,Fsince the Second World War.
OL,11,FThe plans for the site are part of the
OL,12,FLabour government's plan to end the
OL,13,Fuse of hotels to house asylum seekers.
OL,15,FThe Home Office announced the closure
OL,16,Fof 20 more so-called migrant hotels
OL,17,Facross the country, including in
OL,18,FEssex, Kent, West Sussex, Berkshire
OL,19,Fand Oxfordshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
