PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782483502
OL,3,CMP 'shocked' by Home Office plan to
OL,4,Chouse migrants at military base
OL,6,FHotels in the South East which are no
OL,7,Flonger housing asylum seekers include:
OL,8,FHoliday Inn Ashford Central, The
OL,9,FCisswood Horsham, Mercure George
OL,10,FReading, The Granby Gravesham, Oxford
OL,11,FWitney Hotel.
OL,13,FMinisters also confirmed their
OL,14,Fintention to keep using the military
OL,15,Fbase in Crowborough, East Sussex, for
OL,16,Fasylum accommodation until 2030
OL,18,FEarlier this year, defence ministers
OL,19,Fsaid there were 725 Armed Forces
OL,20,Fpersonnel and 183 civilian staff
OL,21,Flocated at MOD Bicester.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
