PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782483502
OL,3,CMP 'shocked' by Home Office plan to
OL,4,Chouse migrants at military base
OL,6,FThe New Labour government announced
OL,7,Fplans to construct a purpose-built
OL,8,Fasylum centre in Bicester in 2001. It
OL,9,Fwas cancelled four years later.
OL,11,FThe Home Office has been approached
OL,12,Ffor comment on the concerns raised
OL,13,Fabout the Bicester site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
